column5: is any thing going on at bronte haven't been down there in a while and wondering if there still getting them out there?!?!
I was there about two weeks ago and fish were few and far between, not really sure how it is now.
hmm not sounding to good might have to head other way out to long point for some fatting up pike and bass
Water has been warm, therefore Salmon has been finicky everywhere. So far still bass and pike condition.
